The colours of autumn across the western border of North Macedonia and Greece are captured in this @CopernicusEU  #Sentinel2 image.

Zoom into the features here  https://t.co/EojlE9xaT2 https://t.co/yNTu5aZESu

Spot Saturn this Sunday! 
 
Look out for the ringed planet on Nov. 10 as it passes near the Moon in the night sky. Viewers in the Americas with clear skies can even see them pass within one degree just after dark: https://t.co/jAaLRwfdL4 https://t.co/ulhXDrsgB2
